item.title: Skyjacks: Episode 205
item.description: Orimar, Jonnit, and Gable explore Sorrow's End. They run into a thoroughly unpleasant Readfeather official named Ansom Stone who quickly takes a liking to Orimar's persona. Jonnit and Gable try to learn more about the manufacturing process for Syndicate Crimson as Orimar tries to do some information gathering of his own. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/OSPN2193291028

item.title: *REBROADCAST BONUS* Bigger and better than ever
item.description:
Hello all you Private Parters and welcome back to the podcast where nothing is off limits.


Jamie is off on a well-deserved holiday and so, in his absence, we've dived into the archives and pulled out a bonus episode from this time last year.


Jamie and Alex discuss their New Year's Resolutions, fill each other in on their NYE antics, and also chat about feeling anxious over the Xmas and New Years period... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/8de47081-5017-4be9-8988-d2ef57dd98c7
